ed="T" n="0808a16"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0808a16"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000012759"><placeName>吳郡</placeName><placeName>嘉禾</placeName><placeName>靈光寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A011570">法相</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0808a17"/><persName key="A011570">釋法相</persName>，姓<name>俞</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000012751"><placeName>吳</placeName><placeName>長水</placeName></placeName>人也。<date notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15"><name>天寶</name>中</date>誕育，為<lb
ed="T" n="0808a18"/>孾兒卓異，<date key="j19982791998643" from-iso="+0759-01-01" to-iso="+0759-12-31">七歲</date>投師，受經法三浹旬<ptr type="glossary" target="#g287"/>，誦通<lb
ed="T" n="0808a19"/>《法華》全部。<date key="j20030272003392" from-iso="+0772-01-01" to-iso="+0772-12-31">弱冠</date>往<placeName key="PL000000042147"><placeName>長安</placeName><placeName>安國寺</placeName></placeName>，得滿足戒，<lb
ed="T" n="0808a20"/>即<date notBefore-iso="+0766-12-22" key="j20011912005993" notAfter-iso="+0780-02-14"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0808sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>人</sic><corr>大</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0808sgsz3"/>曆</name>中</date>也。便於<placeName key="PL000000042189">上京</placeName>習毘尼道，諸部同<lb
ed="T" n="0808a21"/>異，無不該綜，涉十一載，蔚成其業。傳法東<lb
ed="T" n="0808a22"/>歸，請學者如林。<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳郡</placeName>太守奏於<placeName key="PL000000009882">開元寺</placeName>置<lb
ed="T" n="0808a23"/>戒壇，<persName key="A011570">相</persName>預臨壇之選。尋充依止<ptr type="glossary" target="#g333"/>，兼眾推為<lb
ed="T" n="0808a24"/>寺綱管，恒施二眾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g571"/>歸戒。行佩漉囊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g82"/>，器不畜<lb
ed="T" n="0808a25"/>長<ptr type="glossary" target="#g288"/>。每有鳥棲于座側，馳斥不去。<date key="j20282982028298" when-iso="+0841-03-10"><name>會昌</name>元年<lb
ed="T" n="0808a26"/>二月十日</date>午時三刻，告弟子<persName key="A011575">清濬</persName>、<persName key="A011577">清高</persName>：「<ref type="person" target="#A011570">吾</ref>當<lb
ed="T" n="0808a27"/>滅矣。」儼然累足右脇而逝。時眾晝聞管絃<lb
ed="T" n="0808a28"/>清亮，乃天樂也；夕覩異光。春秋八十九，僧臘<lb
ed="T" n="0808a29"/>六十九。<date from-iso="+0841-04-29" key="j20283482028377" to-iso="+0841-05-28">四月</date>遷塔于<placeName key="PL000000058028">來蘇鄉</placeName>之原，白塔是也。<pb ed="T" n="0808b" xml:id="T50.2061.0808b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0808b01"/>後弟子率<placeName key="PL000000058030">義州</placeName><ptr target="#n1860"/>刺史<persName key="A011585">曹信</persName>、大理司直<persName key="A011587">吳方</persName>重<lb
ed="T" n="0808b02"/>修塔，發之，見<persName key="A011570">相</persName>遺骨若銅色，舌相不壞若<lb
ed="T" n="0808b03"/>芙蓉焉，齒全四十二。香湯沐之，重葬，蓋<date key="j20473872047387" when-iso="+0893-06-14"><name>景<lb
ed="T" n="0808b04"/>福</name>二年癸丑歲五月二十二日</date>也。<persName key="A011577">高</persName>弟子<persName key="A011591">公<lb
ed="T" n="0808b05"/>靜</persName>，<persName key="A011591">靜</persName>弟子<persName key="A011593">行蘊</persName>，<persName key="A011593">蘊</persName>弟子<persName key="A011595">仁表</persName>，<persName key="A011595">表</persName>弟子<persName key="A011596">玄杲</persName>，<persName key="A011596">杲</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0808b06"/>本清白<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g814"/>之僧也，同<persName key="A011604">鴻啟</persName>重修<placeName key="PL000000012759">靈光</placeName>一寺，為<lb
ed="T" n="0808b07"/>兵革殘毀之後也。<persName key="A011596">杲<roleName>公</roleName></persName>、<persName key="A011604">啟<roleName>公</roleName></persName>後偕隱<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0808b08"/>習禪觀，相次終于山，焚之皆獲舍利焉。<ptr target="#n1861"/></p>
